This is a file telling how to install PHPUnit and how to use it.

Installation
PHPUnit should be installed using the PEAR Installer.

1 "sudo pear upgrade PEAR" usually suffices to upgrade an existing PEAR installation.
  Following two commands explain how to perform a fresh installation of PEAR.
  (1) wget http://pear.php.net/go-pear.phar
  (2) php go-pear.phar

2 The following two commands (which you may have to run as root) are all that is required
  to install PHPUnit using the PEAR Installer:
  (1) pear config-set auto_discover 1
  (2) pear install pear.phpunit.de/PHPUnit


Usage
1 Enter directory tests/ (probably is current working directory),input command
  "phpunit SinaStorageServiceTest.php",this can test all test cases in file
  SinaStorageServiceTest.php.
2 For more information: http://www.phpunit.de/manual/current/en/textui.html

